snippet: Westbrook had 36 points, 11 rebounds and 6 assists to help the Thunder hold off the visiting Bulls, and he finished without a triple-double for only the third time in his last nine games.
abstract: NBA Roundup; Oklahoma city Thunder beats Chicago Bulls, 109-100; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Westbrook had 36 points, 11 rebounds and 6 assists to help the Thunder hold off the visiting Bulls, and he finished without a triple-double for only the third time in his last nine games.

headline.main: Russell Westbrook Has 36 Points and Key Assist to Lift Thunder
